item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: You can find password from "My Downloadable Products" under "My Account" on our website, next to download link.

item.title: Where is my Template/Product to Download ?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: You can download your product from "My Downloadable Products" under "My Account" on our website.

item.title: Error to extract ZIP File, I can not extract ZIP file even I have password.
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Please make sure you are using Windows PC to extract ZIP file.

item.title: I need my own theme and setup an ecommerce store, can you help me?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Not only the theme, but we provide all services for setup an ecommerce stores. Contact us for magento theme customization and ecommerce store setup. Ask us Quote for professional magento services.

item.title: My download is expired. How can I download again ?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Please contact our support center with your Order number and our team will reset your download link.

item.title: How do I get my download?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: After complete your payment Instant Download link will be available. You can download your products from the "My Downloadable Product" under "My Account". Also There is a link on top of the website "My Downloads". You can download your products from there.

item.title: Download Link not work
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: If there is problem with download you can email us at support [at] templatemela [dot] com.

item.title: What will be included in my purchased products?
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: If you have purchased themes, we will provide Theme Files, Font files and PSD Files (Photoshop files) and Installation Manual. We also provide free installation. But if you still need guide you can contact our live support for any questions.

item.title: I am not getting any reply from Your Company
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: Sometimes, emails goes to SPAM, so also check your SPAM(JUNK) mails. If you haven't receive any email from us email us at support [at] templatemela [dot] com.
